extends layout

block content
  h1(style="color: #f78da7; text-align: center;") Verify Your Email for Pouch
  p Hello #{firstName},
  p Thank you for signing up for Pouch, your Personal Budget Tracker! To complete your registration and start tracking your finances, please verify your email by clicking the link below.
  
  a(href=url, style="background-color: #f78da7; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;") Verify Email

  p(style="margin-top: 20px;") Once verified, you'll be able to access all the features Pouch has to offer, including expense tracking, income management, and budget planning.
  
  p(style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;") If you did not create an account, please ignore this email.